            >
              <Icon name="mdi:sparkles" class="pink-icon" />
            </div>
            <h3
              class="mb-2 md:text-2xl text-xl font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-white"
            >
              Priya Sharma
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              BreastDoc has been a lifesaver for me. The AI insights and doctor
              support helped me make informed decisions about my treatment. I
